file.name: enricher-with-query-params.yml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: Simple API overview
  version: 2.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://petstore.swagger.io/v1
paths:
  /someService/someSubPath/{pathParam1}/otherSubPath/{pathParam2}:
    get:
      operationId: getComponentsByAccount
      x-vertx-event-bus: components_by_account.myapp
      summary: Get the Components by accountNo.
      tags:
        - Category1
        - Default
      externalDocs:
        url: https://touk.pl
      parameters:
        - name: pathParam1
          in: path
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int64
          required: true
        - name: pathParam2
          in: path
          schema:
            type: string
          required: true
        - name: queryParam1
          in: query
          schema:
            type: array
            items:
              type: integer
          required: false
        - name: queryParam2
          in: query
          schema:
            type: boolean
          required: false
        - name: queryParam3
          in: query
          schema:
            type: object
            properties:
              NAME:
                type: string
          required: false

      responses:
        '200':
          description:
            Returns ComponentsByAccount.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Component'
components:
  schemas:
    Component:
      type: object
      properties:
        NAME:
          type: string
